        "title": {
          "type": "text",
          "$t": "Slovanská svätyňa v Moste pri Bratislave 3D"
        },
        "content": {
          "type": "html",
          "$t": "<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\nPredstavujeme Vám 3D vizualizáciu možného vzhľadu <a href=\"http://www.hradiska.sk/search/label/Most%20pri%20Bratislave%20-%20Prv%C3%A1%20staroslovansk%C3%A1%20sv%C3%A4ty%C5%88a%20na%20Slovensku\" target=\"_blank\">pohanskej svätyne, ktorá bola objavená v Moste pri Bratislave.</a> Tvorcom je náš spolupracovník Igor Furugláš, ktorý tento model vytvoril pre našu stránku. Patrí mu za to veľká vďaka.<br />\n<br />\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"tr-caption-container\" style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; text-align: center;\"><tbody>\n<tr><td style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEj1S44Ay4QcQQQ6EfAOdoORW9C6EC0ppXwV9O3xH1G7qKVeopbxEsjIgp1IhssXTQN_ZdWMb-K_oOa66tzlhQ0Pbe19N-FSLtRpgykciGlNBEacWlddBaV7ald-GT-QuAyNabEZXGUm0X0/s1600/Sva%25CC%2588tyn%25CC%258Ca+v+hmle.jpg\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"153\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEj1S44Ay4QcQQQ6EfAOdoORW9C6EC0ppXwV9O3xH1G7qKVeopbxEsjIgp1IhssXTQN_ZdWMb-K_oOa66tzlhQ0Pbe19N-FSLtRpgykciGlNBEacWlddBaV7ald-GT-QuAyNabEZXGUm0X0/s320/Sva%25CC%2588tyn%25CC%258Ca+v+hmle.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></td></tr>\n<tr><td class=\"tr-caption\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Svätyňa v tajomnom opare ... </td></tr>\n</tbody></table>\nVychádzali sme z nám dostupných podkladov, najmä z článkov archeológa Vladimíra Turčana, ktorý svätyňu preskúmal. Oproti exaktnej rekonštrukcii sme toho názoru, že svätyňa by mala byť ohradená prinajmenšom ľahkým prúteným plotom, ktorý tak symbolicky oddeľoval posvätný svet od toho profánneho. Ohradenie svätýň máme dokumentované aj v v prípade iných lokalít, a teda máme za to, že podobne to mohlo byť aj v Moste. Tento prvok však nebol archeologicky doložený, čo však je pochopiteľné, ak plot nebol masívny a mal iba jednoduchšiu konštrukciu.&nbsp; <br />\n<br />\n<div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\">\n<a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgyPwU0P3XNSqj-r7WuNTOM_GZdePJVrZCWB_BHI1zdRRQ2BHiFnc6IOMwM63onZjsifjClUEI4FofvKSDeugIf_ZeS7iIemSUw191QNHU4p6QCXsz2ji7DS0hMUdInc0JtMLigXlb6kJND/s1600/25508183_2011550385787124_6304835047558141522_n.jpg\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" data-original-height=\"466\" data-original-width=\"960\" height=\"155\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgyPwU0P3XNSqj-r7WuNTOM_GZdePJVrZCWB_BHI1zdRRQ2BHiFnc6IOMwM63onZjsifjClUEI4FofvKSDeugIf_ZeS7iIemSUw191QNHU4p6QCXsz2ji7DS0hMUdInc0JtMLigXlb6kJND/s320/25508183_2011550385787124_6304835047558141522_n.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<br />\n<div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\">\n<a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhyCvFGqN5SETLgNnqIhXh3HAYeRnaTqLt15EOG0AL2dqZVut7r8-FqAeE7OSTt5XsweCFSd9LfBabgckdPjOwbZ4EWpX0ShsJv0VkU2Z1i7QuEnSd0g_sISTOQ92PfUhlnN1MMe2viYlqV/s1600/25550151_2011550395787123_2687541250779390787_n.jpg\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" data-original-height=\"508\" data-original-width=\"960\" height=\"169\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhyCvFGqN5SETLgNnqIhXh3HAYeRnaTqLt15EOG0AL2dqZVut7r8-FqAeE7OSTt5XsweCFSd9LfBabgckdPjOwbZ4EWpX0ShsJv0VkU2Z1i7QuEnSd0g_sISTOQ92PfUhlnN1MMe2viYlqV/s320/25550151_2011550395787123_2687541250779390787_n.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<br />\n<div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\">\n<a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhTK5hT2nl2N43I1oKL2c9htPWDkLwiHiOwQYoPM4SizAx31FA8-LfETA-YiO6hgBZnjKo1TQ69YXo_iEP_tbt0CTnNqtN6fEn8t1HKGy_UfvRTiTeQIt2IYw1GYPzcl6h_HigdZ9G5MPqY/s1600/25552199_2011550392453790_6823873462091394663_n.jpg\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" data-original-height=\"458\" data-original-width=\"960\" height=\"152\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhTK5hT2nl2N43I1oKL2c9htPWDkLwiHiOwQYoPM4SizAx31FA8-LfETA-YiO6hgBZnjKo1TQ69YXo_iEP_tbt0CTnNqtN6fEn8t1HKGy_UfvRTiTeQIt2IYw1GYPzcl6h_HigdZ9G5MPqY/s320/25552199_2011550392453790_6823873462091394663_n.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<br />\n<div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\">\n<a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgOav0KZp40oNH_6RYrDTCKJxeFMT9Pp213_MnN_wn1s9eft5Rs_Wt58XUmUxWdLusphIMrAZ2uWzvxqQvPrZXdefmTGFBU7GPmoA9Ira2uLgunByJSR7bDg4pLPM0imyd1ttqmahNL5x9V/s1600/25591600_2011550425787120_5288724196387634354_n.jpg\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" data-original-height=\"521\" data-original-width=\"960\" height=\"173\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgOav0KZp40oNH_6RYrDTCKJxeFMT9Pp213_MnN_wn1s9eft5Rs_Wt58XUmUxWdLusphIMrAZ2uWzvxqQvPrZXdefmTGFBU7GPmoA9Ira2uLgunByJSR7bDg4pLPM0imyd1ttqmahNL5x9V/s320/25591600_2011550425787120_5288724196387634354_n.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<br />\n<div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\">\n<a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgR4VfmfQ8NRbcEhMBdYe3YKctC-eJuaCWwAJbc3WTuPAbh07fU2I9p3GhI67uYX2S5hXg5G3ZvlvLo0GK5cBusKJ1OtILMpS1eSr03602nfVCKTOCBv2hkFlwdxWmJeFkPD-wtiogV0HMj/s1600/25591699_2011550422453787_1977699038862818520_n.jpg\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" data-original-height=\"474\" data-original-width=\"960\" height=\"158\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgR4VfmfQ8NRbcEhMBdYe3YKctC-eJuaCWwAJbc3WTuPAbh07fU2I9p3GhI67uYX2S5hXg5G3ZvlvLo0GK5cBusKJ1OtILMpS1eSr03602nfVCKTOCBv2hkFlwdxWmJeFkPD-wtiogV0HMj/s320/25591699_2011550422453787_1977699038862818520_n.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<br />\n<div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\">\n<a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEiAw_uksQp3QGBt7rUpFulZfvJyXLn8qntcDhKZ3LOxKf5fGIWtpGrs8L3uKuh7e4S2VMehYAEeOPZ66SYywdKRsHON4VhA5XmGN2h7n0m4gmXxXg-POV-1dcVwwISN8XTGIYD34rdISW-P/s1600/25659536_2011550485787114_1435585531978057865_n.jpg\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" data-original-height=\"540\" data-original-width=\"960\" height=\"180\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEiAw_uksQp3QGBt7rUpFulZfvJyXLn8qntcDhKZ3LOxKf5fGIWtpGrs8L3uKuh7e4S2VMehYAEeOPZ66SYywdKRsHON4VhA5XmGN2h7n0m4gmXxXg-POV-1dcVwwISN8XTGIYD34rdISW-P/s320/25659536_2011550485787114_1435585531978057865_n.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<br />\n<div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\">\n<a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgZPr53wzSE_exn05B10FOFb-ZZbEeOTVoS4Lz21XjYFHq8Kobxxf2sD-82dOMrVWIzhRJH_mfLU80PvCqHmEt1u0kC_wCI_GIH-VGEgsgTLpQsFQWlmMubUEpw4VhtuHyoYTrN3ZrWThh9/s1600/25660195_2011550429120453_5553577418808683261_n.jpg\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" data-original-height=\"498\" data-original-width=\"960\" height=\"166\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgZPr53wzSE_exn05B10FOFb-ZZbEeOTVoS4Lz21XjYFHq8Kobxxf2sD-82dOMrVWIzhRJH_mfLU80PvCqHmEt1u0kC_wCI_GIH-VGEgsgTLpQsFQWlmMubUEpw4VhtuHyoYTrN3ZrWThh9/s320/25660195_2011550429120453_5553577418808683261_n.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<br /></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<br /></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\nPoprechádzajte sa po pohanskej svätyni našich slovanských predkov, ktorí v nej pred&nbsp; 1300 rokmi uctievali starobylých slovanských bohov......<br />\n<br />\n<div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\">\n<iframe width=\"320\" height=\"266\" class=\"YOUTUBE-iframe-video\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/v6pIyCJeN6I/0.jpg\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/v6pIyCJeN6I?feature=player_embedded\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe></div>\n<br /></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<br /></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<iframe allowfullscreen=\"\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/4eLfXhhNGOs\" width=\"560\"></iframe><br /></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n</div>\n"
